Subject: Confused user' workstation name
Description:
We have an user login and use to a workstation named LT303, but the Endpoint Protector shows he uses LT302 sometimes. I checked "Computer" under "Device Control" and found LT302 and LT303 (both have agent EPP installed) cannot appear at the same time. Please help to check.

Thanks, Tony
What_We_Know__c: Two computers that are not even in the same subnet or geographic location, appear to have the same user logged in, and when it happens, the other computer just disappears from the console and DB
Next_Steps__c: R&D suggested enabling virtual desktop clone and checking again. waiting for the customer
Solution_Comment__c: enabling virtual desktop clone resolved the issue.
